[{},{"attrs":{"title":"API: The transition Property","description":"Set the default properties of the page transitions."},"body":"<h1><a id=\"the-transition-property\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#the-transition-property\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>The transition Property</h1><ul>\n<li>Type: <code>String</code> or <code>Object</code></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Used to set the default properties of the page transitions.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Default:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\">{\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'page'</span>,\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">mode</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'out-in'</span>\n}</code></pre><p>Example (<code>nuxt.config.js</code>):</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">transition</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'page'</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// or</span>\n  transition: {\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'page'</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">mode</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'out-in'</span>,\n    beforeEnter (el) {\n      <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Before enter...'</span>);\n    }\n  }\n}</code></pre><p>The transition key in <code>nuxt.config.js</code> is used to set the default properties for the page transitions. To learn more about the available keys when the <code>transition</code> key is an object, see the <a href=\"/api/pages-transition#object\">pages transition property</a>.</p>\n<h1><a id=\"the-layouttransition-property\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#the-layouttransition-property\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>The layoutTransition Property</h1><ul>\n<li>Type: <code>String</code> or <code>Object</code></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Used to set the default properties of the layout transitions. Configurations are same as <code>layout</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Default:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\">{\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'layout'</span>,\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">mode</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'out-in'</span>\n}</code></pre><p>Example (<code>nuxt.config.js</code>):</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">layoutTransition</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'layout'</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// or</span>\n  layoutTransition: {\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'layout'</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">mode</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'out-in'</span>\n  }\n}</code></pre><p>Example global <code>css</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.layout-enter-active</span>, <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.layout-leave-active</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transition</span>: opacity .<span class=\"hljs-number\">5s</span>\n}\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.layout-enter</span>, <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.layout-leave-active</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">opacity</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n}</code></pre>","docLink":"https://github.com/nuxt/docs/blob/master/en/api/configuration-transition.md"}]